narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Interesting material, well organized lectures. And robots!!
Very good and interesting class, covers a lot of the same material as AI did. Not that much work until the end of the semester, where the final project can be kind of crazy but also very interesting.
I recommend it if your a CS major looking for a relatively easy elective. It's interesting though so you won't fall asleep with boredom. Not for someone who wants to build robots though.
